            <title>Apple 以 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄【有片睇】手冢治虫短片作品《Midnight》</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/iphone-shooting/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-shooting</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/iphone-shooting/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蒋纳偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222769</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 今日发布了一段完全使用 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄的短片《Midnight》，作为全球 Shot on iPhone 企划的一部分。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2301121_iphone15_a10-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2301121_iphone15_a10-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2301121_iphone15_a10-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>由导演三池崇史将「漫画之神」手冢治虫的隐藏杰作《Midnight》拍成影片，著名演员贺来贤人、小泽征悦和加藤小夏主演。利用 iPhone 15 Pro Max 的镜头捕捉了东京的夜景，拍摄出一部 19 分钟短片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/12-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/12-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/12.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2301110_iphone15_a64-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2301110_iphone15_a64-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2301110_iphone15_a64-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>「Midnight」是一位深夜计程车司机的名字，由著名演员贺来贤人饰演，他在东京街头漫步，向有需要的人士伸出援手。Midnight 遇到一名加藤小夏饰演的年轻女子为了夺回已故父亲的货车生意，而与小泽征悦饰演的黑帮首领发生冲突。他为了帮助加藤小夏脱离困境，在霓虹灯闪烁的东京街头进行一场惊心动魄的汽车追逐，所有场景都利用 iPhone 15 Pro Max 相机拍摄。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/13-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/13-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/13.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_45579"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xd_LmXNBz5w?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xd_LmXNBz5w">YouTube</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/iphone-shooting/mobile-phone/">Apple 以 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄【有片睇】手冢治虫短片作品《Midnight》</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
