            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="p3">节能减碳已成为全球大趋势，为爱地球尽一分力，环保能源将会在未来成为城市重要动力。想知道未来环保能源如何融入社会，大家可进入中电元宇宙 <a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$">CLP TomorroVerse</a> 世界更深入体验。而现在中电更大送奖品，只要完成任务，即有机会获得 CLP Nanobricks 模型！</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222374" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1-694x461.png" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1-694x461.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/englishlogowithchine-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222372" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clp_miniland.jpg 819w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><p class="p3">中电元宇宙 <a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$">CLP TomorroVerse</a> 是一个以环保能源为动力，为动物与人类提供和谐共存的社区。里面有不少关卡，透过精彩刺激的游戏，让大人小朋友都可学习未来环保能源，如何协助我们节能减碳。立即登上中电的元宇宙飞船，一齐去探险吧。</p><p>点击活动网址进入：<a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CLP TomorroVerse</a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240201at.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222392" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse020sc.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">投入元宇宙世界三步曲</h2><p class="p3">元宇宙毋须任何数码货币帐户，你只要<a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.sandbox.game/en/experiences/TomorroVerse/0472219c-ef0f-4b0b-90d4-983cada878af/page/__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EpxRYSOw$">按此</a>打开元宇宙页面，在 The Sandbox 内轻松以 Google 登入或者以电邮建立帐户，再下载与安装好 Sandbox 电脑版（提供 Windows/macOS 版本），即可进入中电元宇宙 CLP TomorroVerse。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222377" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01-633x580.png" alt="" width="633" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01-633x580.png 633w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_01.png 982w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 633px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02-618x580.png" alt="" width="618" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02-618x580.png 618w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_02.png 682w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 618px" /></a></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲The Sandbox 你只需登入 Google 帐户或者用电邮申请帐户，即可投入元宇宙世界（当然亦可连结电子钱包）</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1-694x411.png" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1-694x411.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_04-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲在网页上你就可建立属于自己的分身</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1-694x428.png" alt="" width="694" height="428" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1-694x428.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/loginstruction_10-1.png 1032w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再于电脑（Windows/macOS）安装好 The Sandbox 档案，即可投入元宇宙世界</p><h2 class="p3">探索未来环保能源，玩任务赢礼品</h2><p class="p3">在中电元宇宙 CLP TomorroVerse 世界，大人小朋友都可一齐探索低碳生活模式。透过不同好玩任务，为爱护环境、支持环保能源出一分力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222536 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/evcar-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/evcar-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/evcar-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲你知道未来世界中，电动车的剩余能源有甚么用吗?</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222538 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/visionarygallery-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/visionarygallery-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/visionarygallery-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲<span style="font-weight: 400;">在</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Visionary Gallery </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">你可参观到过往中电活动的作品</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222539 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/solar-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/solar-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/solar-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲玩家要建设好太阳能发电设施</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222540 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/wind-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/wind-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/wind-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲为启动元宇宙风力发电，玩家要深入海底解开机关</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222541 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fish-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fish-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fish-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲在海中畅泳与海龟、小鱼作伴</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222542 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ecofun-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ecofun-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/ecofun-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲<span style="font-weight: 400;">在 ECO Fun Garden 学习低碳知识</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1222544 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/boat-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/boat-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/boat-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="p3" style="text-align: center;">▲<span style="font-weight: 400;">乘坐会飞的中电工程车回去飞船</span></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222393" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/clptomorroverse030sc.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲参与任务可获得不同道具</p><h2 class="p3">限时大放送<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>完成任务赢特色礼品</h2><p class="p3">马上投入中电元宇宙 CLP TomorroVerse 探索未来能源新趋势，现在你更可赢取 CLP Nanobricks 模型。由 2024 年 3 月 6 日起，首 100 名完成所有任务并填写好表格的参加者，将获得造型可爱而设计精致的 CLP Nanobricks 模型*（款式包括男工程师、女工程师，及中电紧急服务工程车。款式将随机发送）。</p><p class="p3">把握机会，马上按此轻松投入中电元宇宙，赢取特色礼品吧！</p><p>点击活动网址进入：<a href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/www.clp.com.hk/zh/education-development/CLPTomorroVerse__;!!MOA0!ejVNo5NaOuHnRpkIda3UQ5ElAX9xZnMcxpWLp4wPL6W1ZISvuAsMLprr_qzmO6JtyIR8ScaazoVQrmHSdo9EEy0Ydss$" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CLP TomorroVerse</a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-694x511.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="511" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-694x511.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8615-scaled.jpg 1223w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1222396" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-694x538.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="538" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-694x538.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2p1a8670-scaled.jpg 1161w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 6